ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: At what time did you settle down for the night? Hours
At what time did you settle down for the night? Minutes
At what time did you fall asleep last night? Hours
At what time did you fall asleep last night? Minutes
At what time did you finally wake this morning? Hours
At what time did you finally wake this morning? Minutes
At what time did you get up this morning? Hours
At what time did you get up this morning? Minutes
Was your sleep:
Notes: 1=Very light; 2=Light; 3=Fairly light; 4=Light average; 5=Deep average; 6=Fairly deep; 7=Deep; 8=Very deep

ElementDescription: How many times did you wake up?
Notes: Number of times; 7=More than six times

ElementDescription: How much sleep did you have last night? Hours
How much sleep did you have last night? Minutes
How much sleep did you have during the day yesterday? Hours
How much sleep did you have during the day yesterday? Minutes
How well did you sleep last night?
If you did not sleep well, what was the trouble?
How clear-headed did you feel after getting up this morning?
Notes: 1=Still very drowsy; 2=Still moderately drowsy; 3=Still slightly drowsy; 4=Fairly clear-headed; 5=Alert; 6=Very alert

ElementDescription: How satisfied were you with last night's sleep?
Were you troubled by waking early and being unable to get off to sleep again?
How much difficulty did you have in getting off to sleep last night?
How long did it take you to fall asleep last night? Hours
How long did it take you to fall asleep last night? Minutes
